<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/customer/customer.css"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 100%;
        }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .sidebar {
            flex-basis: 20%;
            color: #fff;
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #333;
        }
        p{
            font-size: 30px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        .mainpage {
            flex-basis: 80%;
            border: 1px solid darkgreen;
            padding: 1rem;

        }
        .menu_title{
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            width: 1000px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .menu_sub{
            background-color: orange;
            width: 1000px;
            height: 30px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        #btn_menu{
            width: 100px;
            height: 30px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-left: 50px;

        }
        .menu1{
            /* border: 1px solid black; */
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 1000px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .image h2{
            text-align:left;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        #menu1_name{
            background-color: oldlace;
            width: 250px;
            height: 25px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: large;
        }
        #menu1_price{
            background-color: oldlace;
            width: 250px;
            height: 25px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: large;
        }
        #menu1_context{
            background-color: oldlace;
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: large;
        }
        .image{
            /* border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px; */
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            width: 1000px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            /* font-size: 30px; */
        }
        #btn_addmenu{
            width: 300px;
            height: 40px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        h5 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        ul li a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        ul li a:hover {
            color: white;
        }
        #btn_submit, #btn_cancel{
            width: 500px;
            height: 40px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .finish_space{
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<main class="container">
    <aside class="sidebar">
        <p>사장님 페이지</p>
        <h5> > 가게 정보</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="StoreAdd.mustache">가게 등록</a></li>
            <li><a href="StoreEdit.mustache">가게 수정</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">리뷰 관리</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h5> > 매출 관리</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="#">오늘의 매출</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">월 매출</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">년 매출</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h5> > 예약 관리</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="#">이번 주 예약</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">지난 예약</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h5> > 공지 사항</h5>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">서비스 소개</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
        </ul>
    </aside>
    <table class="table">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">이름</th>
            <th scope="col">가격</th>
            <th scope="col">설명</th>
            <th scope="col">인기</th>
            <th scope="col">사진</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {{#menu}}
            <tr>
                <th>{{id}}</th>
                <td>{{price}}</td>
                <td>{{content}}</td>
                <td>{{popular}}</td>
                <td>{{photo}}</td>

            </tr>
        {{/menu}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <a href="/menu/{{id}}/edit" class="btn btn-primary">수정하기</a>
    <a href="/menu/{{id}}/delete" class="btn btn-danger">삭제하기</a>
    <a href="/menu" class="btn btn-primary">목록가기</a>
</main>
<script>
    function readURL(input) {
        if (input.files && input.files[0]) {
            var reader = new FileReader();
            reader.onload = function(e) {
                document.getElementById('preview').src = e.target.result;
            };
            reader.readAsDataURL(input.files[0]);
        } else {
            document.getElementById('preview').src = "";
        }
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>